data.description: Gorgeous one story white brick home in Lakeshore on a cul de sac.   Walk in to a beautiful setting and open foyer.  Secondary bedrooms at the front of the home.   Which all secondary rooms have brand new carpet.   On the right enjoy your Media Room.  It can be used at your discretion as a second living area, fitness or play room.   Large dining room  to seat 10-12 with an entrance to the kitchen.  Beautiful kitchen with stainless steal appliances and large island with sink.  The island has breakfast bar seating as well as a place for your dinette table. Kitchen opens to the family room which is great for entertaining.  Gas log fireplace and lots of windows that offer natural light.   The homeowners retreat is at the back of the home.  It is very spacious with a shower and separate tub.  2 walk in closets and vanity has double sinks.  The primary bedroom has a private access to the luxurious pool and hot tub. Seller is offering a concession for new oven and microwave.
